<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/root.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/legal.css') }}">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='assets/images/logos/LogoBrand.png') }}" type="image/png">

</head>
<body>
    {% include "snippets/navbar.jinja" %}

    <main class="legal-main">
        <section class="legal-container">
            <header class="legal-header">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="legal-subtitle">Last Updated: 15th of March, 2026</p>
            </header>

            <div class="legal-content-card">
                <h3>1. General Information</h3>
                <p>
                    The protection of your personal data is of particular concern to me. I process your data exclusively on the basis of the legal provisions (GDPR/DSGVO, TKG 2021). In this privacy policy, I inform you about the most important aspects of data processing within the framework of my website.
                </p>

                <h3>2. Contacting Me</h3>
                <p>
                    If you contact me via the contact form at <a href="/contact" class="legal-link">/contact</a> or by e-mail, the data you provide (such as your name, e-mail address, and message content) will be stored for a period of six months for the purpose of processing the inquiry and in the event of follow-up questions. I do not pass on this data without your consent.
                </p>

                <h3>3. Web Hosting & Infrastructure</h3>
                <p>
                    My website is hosted on <strong>Render.com</strong> (Render Services, Inc.). When you visit this website, Render may process technical data (Log Files) such as your IP address, browser type, and time of access to ensure the security and stability of the service. This represents a legitimate interest according to Art. 6 Para. 1 lit. f GDPR. I have concluded a Data Processing Agreement (DPA) with the provider where necessary.
                </p>

                <h3>4. Cookies & Analytics</h3>
                <p>
                    <strong>Session Cookies:</strong> This website uses strictly necessary session cookies. These are required for technical functions like login management and are deleted when your browser session ends.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>First-Party Analytics:</strong> I use a self-developed, privacy-friendly analytics tool. This tool tracks page views and duration of stay. All data is <strong>fully anonymized</strong> before storage; no unique identifiers or full IP addresses are saved, meaning no personal reference can be established.
                </p>

                <h3>5. External Services & Web Fonts</h3>
                <p>
                    For the consistent and appealing display of content, this website uses <strong>Google Fonts</strong> and <strong>FontAwesome</strong>. 
                </p>
                <p>
                    <em>Important Note:</em> When you access a page, your browser connects to the servers of Google (USA) and FontAwesome (USA) to load the fonts. In this process, your IP address is technically transferred to these providers. This processing is based on my legitimate interest in a professional online presentation (Art. 6 Para. 1 lit. f GDPR).
                </p>

                <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
                <p>
                    You generally have the rights to information, correction, deletion, restriction, data portability, revocation, and objection. If you believe that the processing of your data violates data protection law or your data protection claims have been violated in any way, you can complain to the supervisory authority. In Austria, this is the <strong>Österreichische Datenschutzbehörde (DSB)</strong>.
                </p>

                <blockquote class="legal-disclaimer">
                    <p><strong>Contact for Privacy Matters:</strong><br>
                    Jackstar<br>
                    <a href="mailto:jackstarhimself@gmail.com" class="legal-link">jackstarhimself@gmail.com</a></p>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <script src="{{url_for('static', filename='js/global.js') }}"></script>
    {% include "snippets/footer.jinja" %}
</body>
</html>